Aha Assan (Arabic, Hebrew), nke a na-ejikwa mgbagwoju anya ma  jiri ya mee ihe dị ka Hassan, bụ aha nna Arab, Anglo-Saxon na Ghanaian. Ọ bụ ihe a na-ahụkarị n'etiti ndị Ghana na akụkụ ụfọdụ nke Europe
A pụkwara ịchọta aha nna ahụ n'etiti ndị Lebanese gbara ọsọ ndụ si Ndịda  Amerika bụ ndị gbanwere aha nna ha n'ihi agha ahụ, yana ndị Romanian.
